353
00:23:09,156 --> 00:23:10,864
One, two, three.

354
00:23:13,445 --> 00:23:14,544
How about here?

355
00:23:15,223 --> 00:23:17,318
It's really nice.

356
00:23:17,318 --> 00:23:18,749
Do you want to have a wedding here?

357
00:23:18,749 --> 00:23:21,440
What are you saying?
