and travel together.

361
00:23:31,895 --> 00:23:34,069
I want to share those moments.

362
00:23:34,069 --> 00:23:35,232
Because of you.

363
00:23:37,901 --> 00:23:39,071
I feel the same way.

364
00:24:12,897 --> 00:24:15,498
(SBC)

